title: Dirk Maassen with Science Teheran - Spiraling
description:
When I wrote this song I knew right from the beginning that Vicente (aka Science Teheran) would have been the perfect match to collab with. So I asked him if he was interested in adding some cello and instrumentation. He joined in and the result was beyond what I expected and touched me really deeply - I hope it will be the same with you !

Vicente Bueso: Keyboard and Magic :-)
Dirk Maassen: Piano

If not yet already done you should visit his cloud: https://soundcloud.com/scienceteheran

imagery by pentalunex.com

www.maassen-music.com

If you like my music please give me a smile and like my Facebook page :-): www.facebook.com/Dirk.Maassen.Music

watch my piano video clips at youtube: www.youtube.com/user/ascoltadi?feature
